divs: sighting detailsi was outside looking in the same area of sky that i filmed my easter ufo sighting and noticed a commercial jet leaving a contrail. when the plane passed directly overhead i noticed a large barbell-shaped object stationary in the sky. i noticed the object become smaller and then back to its original size. then, it slid or glided- from a stationary postion about 1\3 the sky's distance- like on water- and back to its original position. this object was much higher than the haze at high altitude and much higher than air traffic. it was enormous! i could see the object's shading and it appeared to be white. i ran inside after a few minutes, grabbed my video camera and asked my girlfriend to come outside. she saw the object but could not focus on it. i filmed it but the ufo was much too high for my video camera to distinguish and it looks like a white blurry dot in the sky. it may still be there because the thin high clouds covered the object. i am going to keep an eye out.
